3. [test_survey](SKILL/SKILL.test_survey.md) - Assess test coverage
4. [deps_audit](SKILL/SKILL.deps_audit.md) - Audit dependencies

### Security & Compliance
1. [security_scan](SKILL/SKILL.security_scan.md) - Comprehensive security check
2. [deps_audit](SKILL/SKILL.deps_audit.md) - Dependency security audit
3. [repo_recon](SKILL/SKILL.repo_recon.md) - Overall project security posture

### Code Quality Improvement
1. [test_survey](SKILL/SKILL.test_survey.md) - Baseline test coverage
2. [perf_audit](SKILL/SKILL.perf_audit.md) - Performance analysis
3. [refactor_plan](SKILL/SKILL.refactor_plan.md) - Improvement strategy
4. [api_design](SKILL/SKILL.api_design.md) - API quality review

### Custom Skill Development
