## Getting Started

### For New Users
1. Read [DEMO.md](DEMO.md) for quick start guide
2. Try [repo_recon](SKILL/SKILL.repo_recon.md) on your current project
3. Explore [FLOW.onboard.yaml](FLOW/FLOW.onboard.yaml) for automated workflows

### For Advanced Users
1. Use [skill_drafting](SKILL/SKILL.skill_drafting.md) to create custom skills
2. Combine skills into custom pipelines
3. Contribute improvements to the library

### For Teams
1. Standardize on skill usage patterns
2. Create team-specific pipelines
3. Establish quality gates using skills

